extendedInfo.description: The best Dexter soundboard of all your favorite characters. Updated biweekly so even during the off season you will be able to have your favorite characters in the palm of your hand.As always please let us know your favorites that we can include in our next release.

reviews.title: Dexter
reviews.comment: 4 stars for now, love the app but I can\'t set any sounds to a ringtone then it would get 5 stars!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Pretty cool I guess....
reviews.comment: I wish the Dexter quotes were a little bit longer than than just one second though. Now, this is for the big crybaby who wants his 99\302\242 back; its just a f**k**g dollar! Who gives a s**t!

reviews.comment: I installed it and it doesn\'t work at all. Uninstalling now. Uninstalled and reinstalled it. Still doesn\'t work. It\'s crap. I want my money back.
